---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout 
    title="Servicios Digitales: Web, SEO, E-commerce y Marketing | SEMTIC" 
    description="Diseño web, e-commerce, SEO, gestión de redes sociales y campañas digitales. Servicios diseñados para que tu negocio venda más."
    image="https://semtic.cl/og-servicios.png">

    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#2dd4bf] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
                Nuestros <span class="text-gradient">Servicios</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
                Diseñamos tu página web y potenciamos tu marketing digital para que tu negocio venda más y destaque online.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
                Sitios web modernos, SEO para aparecer mejor en Google y gestión profesional de redes sociales.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Servicios Principales -->
    <section class="py-24 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.3), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.6));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                    Servicios <span class="text-gradient">Principales</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Lo que más piden nuestros clientes, lo más rentable y lo que realmente mueve resultados.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Servicio 1: Diseño y Desarrollo Web -->
            <div class="mb-20">
                <div class="group relative p-10 md:p-12 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#00f2ea]/50 transition-all duration-500">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00f2ea]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#00f2ea] border border-white/10 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,242,234,0.4)] transition-shadow">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)]">Diseño y Desarrollo Web</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Creamos sitios web modernos, rápidos y pensados para convertir visitas en clientes. Diseñamos o actualizamos tu página con contenido claro, diseño intuitivo y optimización para buscadores, para que aparezcas mejor en Google y generes más oportunidades reales.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ea]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">E-commerce para aumentar tus ventas online</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ea]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Sitios autoadministrables (actualiza tu contenido fácilmente)</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ea]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Sitios dinámicos y escalables según tu crecimiento</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ea]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Diseño One Page Scroll claro y sin distracciones</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ea]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Páginas enfocadas en servicios, campañas o promociones</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ea]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Optimización SEO inicial para mejorar tu posicionamiento</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-8">
                            <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f2ea] to-[#3b82f6] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-bold tracking-wide hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,242,234,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                                Quiero mejorar mi web
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Servicio 2: Gestión de Redes Sociales -->
            <div class="mb-20">
                <div class="group relative p-10 md:p-12 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#4f46e5]/50 transition-all duration-500">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5] border border-white/10 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(79,70,229,0.4)] transition-shadow">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)]">Gestión de Redes Sociales</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Gestionamos tus redes sociales para que tu marca se vea mejor, llegue a más personas y convierta seguidores en clientes. Creamos contenido profesional, administramos tus perfiles y planificamos estrategias que te ayudan a crecer de manera constante.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Diseño de publicaciones profesionales</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Redacción de contenido alineado a tu marca</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Calendario editorial organizado</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Programación y automatización</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Gestión de anuncios en Facebook e Instagram</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-8">
                            <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4f46e5] to-[#818cf8] rounded-full text-white font-bold tracking-wide hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(79,70,229,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                                Quiero impulsar mis redes
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Servicio 3: Campañas Digitales -->
            <div class="mb-20">
                <div class="group relative p-10 md:p-12 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#39ff14]/50 transition-all duration-500">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14] border border-white/10 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(57,255,20,0.4)] transition-shadow">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 8v8m-4-5v5m-4-2v2m-2 4h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)]">Campañas Digitales (Google Ads + Meta Ads)</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Creamos campañas en Google y redes sociales pensadas para traer clientes reales, no solo clics. Segmentamos correctamente, optimizamos tu presupuesto y medimos resultados para que cada peso invertido genere retorno.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Campañas de búsqueda en Google</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Campañas de alcance y conversión en Meta</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Optimización continua del rendimiento</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14]"></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400">Informes claros y fáciles de entender</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-8">
                            <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#39ff14] to-[#2dd4bf] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-bold tracking-wide hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(57,255,20,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                                Cotiza tu proyecto
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Servicios Complementarios -->
    <section class="py-24 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.6), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.8));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                    Servicios <span class="text-gradient">Complementarios</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Soluciones que fortalecen tu presencia digital, mejoran la comunicación con tus clientes y optimizan procesos internos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Email Marketing -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#00f2ea]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00f2ea]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-2xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#00f2ea] border border-white/10 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,242,234,0.4)] transition-shadow">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)]">Email Marketing & Newsletter</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Para mantener conectados a tus clientes y generar ventas recurrentes. Creamos newsletters y campañas de email marketing que informan, promocionan y fidelizan.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- SAC -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#4f46e5]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-2xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5] border border-white/10 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(79,70,229,0.4)] transition-shadow">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)]">Atención Digital Automatizada (SAC)</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Implementamos respuestas automáticas, flujos de contacto y chatbots que funcionan 24/7. Captar leads incluso cuando no estás disponible.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Integraciones -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#39ff14]/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-2xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14] border border-white/10 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(57,255,20,0.4)] transition-shadow">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)]">Integraciones y Soluciones a Medida</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Desarrollamos soluciones personalizadas: integraciones entre plataformas, paneles de control, funciones internas o herramientas digitales diseñadas según tu proceso real.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Final -->
    <section class="py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.8), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.95));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                ¿Listo para <span class="text-gradient">crecer online</span>?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                Agenda tu diagnóstico gratuito y descubre cómo podemos ayudarte a alcanzar tus objetivos.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <a href="https://wa.me/56988169404?text=Hola,%20quiero%20agendar%20una%20reunión" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#25D366] to-[#3b82f6] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-extrabold text-lg tracking-wide shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(37,211,102,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"/></svg>
                    Agenda una reunión por WhatsApp
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
